reviewText: Have always been a fan of strippers, but this DVD isn't Chippendales quality. Guys are uninteresting. Music sounds like it's from a MIDI file, and the DVD surface itself looks like it was burned and printed on an inkjet printer. Save your money.
Just as the title says it all - male dancers in thongs... and for most of them, see thru thongs as well. tasteful, artistic, and great background video for a party.
The title says it all. I must be a masochist to have purchased this. Putrid and another rip-off.
